@hazelfarm Hello Damon, 
We are really sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. We - the Social Media Team, can unfortunately not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding. 
Best regards, Gayle

@Frranz_Brandl Hallo Franz,
ich kann deine Verärgerung zwar verstehen, allerdings haben wir hier auf Twitter keinen Zugriff auf die Gepäcksysteme und können daher in diesem Fall leider nicht weiterhelfen.
Viele Grüße, Alessandra

@loek_8 Hello again,
I have answered your previous message.
Best regards, Alessandra

@CelineSpithoven Hello Celine,
I am very sorry to hear about your delayed luggage. We are unable to assist with baggage cases, we kindly ask you to stay in touch with the number on your Lost Report for any updates. You may alternatively check the current status online here
https://t.co/hrzpeJ2Zxa

@FarymaB Hello Faryma,
please contact specialcases@austrian.com
Best regards, Alessandra

@GertraudEckart Liebe Gertraud,
ich kann deine Verärgerung zwar verstehen, allerdings haben wir hier auf Twitter keinen Zugriff auf die Gepäcksysteme und können daher in diesem Fall leider nicht weiterhelfen. Bitte bleibe in Kontakt mit dem zuständigen Team von Lost &amp; Found
Lg,  Alessandra

@mtsullivn [3/3]To file a claim for additional expenses, kindly fill out this online form and attach your receipts. https://t.co/rXJ4j9VHYR  
Again, we apologize for this. 
Best regards, Gayle

@jeffjarvis Hi Jeff, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@marcdeb Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Should your flight be affected by any flight irregularity you will be informed given the fact you have added any contact to your booking.
Best regards, Shawn

@nate_armstead Hello, 
we are very sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. We - the Social Media Team, can unfortunately not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding.
Best regards, Gayle

@jarisalminen Dear Jari
unfortunately, we cannot tell you a specific time of response, since your case has to be handled by various different departments. Still, we can assure you that our colleagues are doing their best to get back to you with news soon!
Best regards, Alessandra

@duck_malakes Hello,
I'm sorry to hear about your experience. Kindly check your credit card statement for a double booking and contact us via this online form https://t.co/KvLtbwEYYs . Please also attach both payment receipts and the credit card statement. 
Best regards, Gayle

@fahadalsareei Hi Fahad, 
Thanks for reaching out to us! Airlines comply with the entry regulations specified by the respective national authorities. More information about international entry/transit regulations are found here https://t.co/ugM6XvfxRx   
Best regards, Gayle

@noonesbhakt Dear Santosh,
we can assure you that our colleagues are doing their best to get back to you with news soon!
Best regards, Alessandra

@partalisarah Hi Sarah,
We are really sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. We - the Social Media Team, can unfortunately not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding.
Best regards, Gayle

@khvanchanok3 Hello,
we understand that the waiting time can be longer than usual but our colleagues will reply as soon as possible to your e-mail, until then we have to kindly ask you for your continued patience. Thank you.
Kind regards, Alessandra

@gradsen @aircanada Hi there AJ,
the bags will be checked through your final destination but the customs check will be held at the first stop in Canada.
Best regards, Alessandra

@SlobodanSarenac Dear Slobodan,
please feel free to seek reimbursement by submitting a claim here: https://t.co/99riI0OUuT. Be sure to include any receipts from additional expenses.
Best regards, Alessandra

@1204charchar Hi Charlotte, 
Thank you for getting in touch. We kindly ask you to use the following link https://t.co/0sMmStae9j and please fill out the online form on our web page for any refund request. 
Best regards, Shawn
